{
  "texts": [
    "However, there are too many issues with this dataset.",
    "(1) First, the audio quality varies by track.",
    "(2) Heavy artist repetition is often ignored during dataset split.",
    "(3) The label is not 100% correct.",
    "To solve this problem and make fair comparison 60, we use a cleaned version and split -\"fault-filtered\" 63, which divides the dataset into train, validation, and test."
  ]
}